IDURAR ERP/CRM vs Mohi ERP - Detailed Analysis
Architecture Comparison
IDURAR ERP/CRM:

Stack: MERN (MongoDB, Express.js, React, Node.js)
Frontend: React 18 + Ant Design (AntD) + Redux for state management
Backend: Node.js + Express.js with Mongoose ODM
