Deployment: Requires MongoDB Atlas or self-hosted MongoDB
Mohi ERP (Current):

Stack: Python Flask + PostgreSQL
Frontend: Jinja2 templates + Tailwind CSS + Alpine.js
Backend: Flask with SQLAlchemy ORM
Database: PostgreSQL (SQL, relational)
Authentication: Flask-Login with session-based auth
Deployment: Docker with docker-compose (single command)
